{"tid":2002341,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【佬訊專欄】記五一黃金周 - 佬訊","createTime":"2020-05-05T06:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T07:35:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43831be5f4a1d4c5b0aa95ba38abbb48717c7d8b","tid":2002341,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"全文 link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200505/ZIGFXV5A3PNUEJDWATQPM3C75M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200505%2FZIGFXV5A3PNUEJDWATQPM3C75M%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=814732f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200505%2FZIGFXV5A3PNUEJDWATQPM3C75M%2F&h=50b911e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200505/ZIGFXV5A3PNUEJDWATQPM3C75M/</a><br />\n<br />\n【佬訊專欄】記五一黃金周 - 佬訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200505/large/1588609891_d887.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200505%2Flarge%2F1588609891_d887.jpg&h=e9848242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如今在香港，有人的地方就有黃店。只要看看哪一間店舖人頭湧湧、哪一間冷冷清清，大概也就知道誰是黃店。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n上個星期連假四天，又適逢五一黃金周，佬編終於忍不住想出街走走，響應號召去黃店大肆消費。<br />\n<br />\n太耐無出街，也不知市況，還儍更更拿着黃app找黃店，後來才發現多此一舉。金庸說有人就有江湖，<span style=\"color: orange;\">而如今在香港，有人的地方就有黃店。只要看看哪一間店舖人頭湧湧、哪一間冷冷清清，大概也就知道誰是黃店。</span><br />\n<br />\n烈日當空................突然有陣涼意，往源頭一看，原來是間中門大開的藍店。<br />\n<br />\n在此先向諸君confess，佬編不爭氣地站在門前涼了一陣子冷氣。乘涼間，隱約聽到店內在說甚麼黑暴、搞事，而事情就是這樣發生。<br />\n<br />\n明明舖內無乜人，但只見老闆漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，望着是是但但的新聞叫嚷道：「垃圾黃店不能說賺&hellip;&hellip;黃店！小眾市場的笑話，還能賺麼？」接連是更難懂的話，甚麼「渺小又卑鄙的幻想」、「經濟上的塔利班」、「消費掛鈎政治」云云，引得佬編的友人都笑了出來。<br />\n<br />\n此時老闆終於發現有兩個活生生的人在門外，便搭話道：「食晏？入嚟坐，有午餐有常餐，凍飲免加價」佬編兩人回過臉去，不再理會................而佬編二人身體終於都涼下來，「下次有機會先啦。」說罷轉身而去。老闆見我們毫不熱心，便嘆一口氣，顯出惋惜的樣子。<br />\n<br />\n「下次睇怕都執笠了。」友人輕聲說，然後《蘋果》突然彈出noti：「喜茶港8間分店只剩兩間」。此刻，佬編只覺心比身體更涼了。<br />\n<br />\n佬訊<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/loshunhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Floshunhk%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=fc748169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/loshunhk/</a>"},{"pid":"1ddc164e8ab78151d2c4179465a17defe1c1fc13","tid":2002341,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"而如今在香港，有人的地方就有黃店。只要看看哪一間店舖人頭湧湧、哪一間冷冷清清，大概也就知道誰是黃店。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fd19af269b548a08986580132b9ee8604b5b56","tid":2002341,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:48:34.000Z","msg":"次次改編孔乙己都好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14000472eca3b9c1a2f4743153ba1d78f4fbb78","tid":2002341,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"「經濟上的塔利班」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51596b037674d39c1e0e78dfeac7c0090d26eaae","tid":2002341,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}